\left|\begin{array}{ccccc} 1 & 1 & \ldots &  & 1\\ 2x_{1} & 2x_{2} &  &  & 2x_{n}\\ \vdots\\ nx_{1}^{n-1} & nx_{2}^{n-1} & \ldots &  & nx_{n}^{n-1}\\ \\ \end{array}\right|
    \det A = \partial_{x_1, x_2, \ldots, x_n} \left( x_1 x_2 \cdots x_n \prod_{i < j} (x_i - x_j) \right) 
    \det A = n! \prod_{i < j} (x_i - x_j) 
